Package it.uniroma2.sel.simlab.jeqn.policies.masks

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MaskBasePolicy<I,E,S,D>
    Defines the root mask class of the mask hierarchy
    MaskExplicitPolicy<E,D>
    Enables the masking of Explicity policies
    MaskImplicitAndExplicitInputDependentPolicy<I,E,D>
    Enables the mapping of policies that depend on implicit and explicit input
    MaskImplicitButNotExplicitInputAndStateDependentPolicy<I,S,D>
    Defines the mask for policies that depend on implicit input and state but do not depend on explicit input
    MaskImplicitButNotExplicitInputDependentPolicy<I,E,D>
    Defines the mask for policies that depend from implicit input, but do not depend on the explcit input
    MaskImplicitPolicy<I,S,D>
    Enables the masking of policies that depend on implicit input
    MaskStateDependentPolicy<E,S,D>
    Defines the mask for policies depending on the internal state
    MaskStateOnlyDependentPolicy<S,D>
    Defines the mask for policies depending on the internal state only
